## 5) Intégration rapide dans ParallaxWidget (exemple)
```vue
<ParallaxWidget
  reverse
  :speed-factor="1"
  :smoothing-ms="0"
  reveal-on-view
  :background-light="[
    { src: '/images/home/home-hero-01/back--light.svg',  speed: 0.10 },
    { src: '/images/home/home-hero-01/mid--light.svg',   speed: 0.18, blendMode: 'screen' },
    { src: '/images/home/home-hero-01/front--light.svg', speed: 0.28 }
  ]"
  :background-dark="[
    { src: '/images/home/home-hero-01/back--dark.svg',  speed: 0.10 },
    { src: '/images/home/home-hero-01/mid--dark.svg',   speed: 0.18, blendMode: 'screen' },
    { src: '/images/home/home-hero-01/front--dark.svg', speed: 0.28 }
  ]"
>
  <!-- Optionnel : SVG inline animé -->
  <!--
  <template #aplats>
    <svg>...</svg>
  </template>
  -->
</ParallaxWidget>
```